<div class="row">
	<div class="col-xs-12">

		<div class="col-xs-12" id="about">
			<h2>Dogparc is a Denver-based service that connects canine professionals to potential clients.</h2>
		</div>

		<div class="well" >
			<div class="row">

				
				<div class="col-sm-6 pull-left" id="aboutdesc">
					<p>Denver is a city famous for dog-lovers. Because of that, we know just how many services our beloved pooches need: And that's why Dogparc exists. From dog trainers, to walkers, to sitters, to new clients for your canine business, you can find anything you're looking for, all within your city. Have a question not covered on this page? <%= link_to "Get in touch.", new_contact_path %></p>
				</div>

				<div class="col-sm-6 pull-right" id="aboutimg">
					<img class="img-responsive" src="/images/doggie.jpg" />
					<p class="caption">Joey's family found him a great sitter here on Dogparc.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="col-sm-6 pull-left" id="aboutdesc">
					<h4>What is a Full Account?</h4>
						<p>A basic account only allows you to preview the names and job titles of our registered users. However, a full account enables you to see full contact information. This allows users to see professional contact information, and also allows professionals to see user contact information to solicit their services.
						</p>
						<%= link_to "Sign up today!", new_user_registration_path(plan: @full_plan.id), class: 'btn btn-default btn-lg btn-block' %>
				</div>

			</div>
		</div>

	</div>
</div>
